OL,5,     GMusic
OL,6,G0340FDrop The Dead Donkey
OL,7,     GIt's party time for GlobeLink:
OL,8,     Gthe razz at the British News
OL,9,     GAwards ceremony begins. Damian
OL,10,     Gdreams of victory, Dave dreams of
OL,11,     GHelen, and for once Henry is less
OL,12,     Gthan happy to be centre-stage.
OL,13,G0405FDrop The Dead Donkey
OL,14,     GAfter a sudden death at
OL,15,     GGlobeLink, Gus goes into exercise
OL,16,     Goverdrive to try to defer his own
OL,17,     Gdemise. Meanwhile, George tries
OL,18,     Ghis hand at acting; and Damien
OL,19,     Ghas trouble with his Porsche.
