OL,8,G0530FJack Hargreaves' Old Country
OL,9,     GWith construction of his road
OL,10,     Gcart complete, Jack arranges for
OL,11,     Git to be decorated. Then on the
OL,12,     Gsite of a hill fort in Dorset he
OL,13,     Gspots many different species of
OL,14,     Gbutterfly.
